This repository is a research software prototype for neoantigen candidate
prioritization and validation planning. It is not a clinical decision system.

The lightweight release does not bundle external bioinformatics tools,
licensed databases, patient data, large references, virtual environments, or
workflow work directories. External tools such as pVACtools, NetMHCpan,
MHCflurry, PRIME, BigMHC, DeepImmuno, STAR-Fusion, FusionCatcher, Arriba,
EasyFuse, GATK, FACETS, ASCAT, and related resources remain governed by their
own licenses, terms, and citation requirements.

Users are responsible for validating installed tool versions, licenses,
reference data provenance, sample consent, and local clinical/research
governance before using real data.
